WEBVTT

00:08:58.504 --> 00:09:00.648
It was the first of many protests.

00:09:01.047 --> 00:09:03.407
The Icelandic prime minister
had to resign.

00:09:03.431 --> 00:09:05.779
It was a first of many resignations.

00:09:06.275 --> 00:09:09.838
We spotlighted many famous people
such as Lionel Messi,

00:09:09.862 --> 00:09:12.190
the most famous
soccer player in the world.

00:09:12.726 --> 00:09:15.016
And there were some
unintended consequences.

00:09:15.454 --> 00:09:19.131
These alleged members
of a Mexican drug cartel were arrested

00:09:19.155 --> 00:09:22.006
after we published details
about their hideout.

00:09:22.615 --> 00:09:24.555
They'd been using the address

00:09:24.579 --> 00:09:26.549
to register their offshore company.

00:09:26.573 --> 00:09:29.368
(Laughter)